criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Sedentary older women according World Health Organization, defined as not performing
             moderate to vigorous physical activity and vigorous for 150 min / week for at least 3
             months;

          -  BMI <to 35.00 kg / m2;

          -  Sign the Informed Consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous diagnosis of Diabetes Mellitus;

          -  Use of any medication for glycemic control;

          -  Orthopedic problems that impair walking or use of orthoses for walking.

          -  Relative or absolute contraindications to perform physical activity.
